MANU/SC/0002/1996

Neutral Citation: 1994 INSC 283

IN THE SUPREME COURT OF INDIA

Civil Appeal Nos. 4947-50 of 1994.

Decided On: 26.07.1994

Tata Cellular Vs. Union of India (UOI)

Hon'ble Judges/Coram:
M.N. Venkatachaliah, CJI., M.M. Punchhi and S. Mohan, JJ.

Counsels:
For Appellant/Petitioner/Plaintiff: Soli J. Sorabjee, M.H. Baig, Ashok Sen, Harish Salve and G.E. Vahanvati, Advs

For Respondents/Defendant: D.P. Gupta, Solicitor General, Anil B. Divan, K. Parasaran, K.K. Venugopal and G. Ramaswamy, Advs.

Subject: Commercial

Subject: Constitution

Mentioned IN

