Cases Referred:
J. Mohapatra and Co. and Ors. vs. State of Orissa and Ors. MANU/SC/0008/1984; Ashok Kumar Yadav and Ors. vs. State of Haryana and Ors. MANU/SC/0026/1985; Sterling Computers Limited and Ors. vs. M & N Publications Limited and Ors. MANU/SC/0439/1993; Union of India (UOI) and Ors. vs. Hindustan Development Corpn. and Ors. MANU/SC/0219/1994; Mahabir Auto Stores and Ors. vs. Indian Oil Corporation and Ors. MANU/SC/0191/1990; Erusian Equipment and Chemicals Ltd. and Ors. vs. State of West Bengal and Ors. MANU/SC/0061/1974; G.B. Mahajan and Ors. vs. The Jalgaon Municipal Council and Ors. MANU/SC/0284/1991; Poddar Steel Corporation vs. Ganesh Engineering Works and Ors. MANU/SC/0363/1991; Vassiliades vs. Vassiliades and another MANU/PR/0066/1944; Ranjit Thakur vs. Union of India (UOI) and Ors. MANU/SC/0691/1987; Charan Lal Sahu vs. Union of India (UOI) MANU/SC/0285/1990; State of Uttar Pradesh and Ors. vs. Dharmander Prasad Singh and Ors. MANU/SC/0563/1989; Fasih Chaudhary vs. Director General, Doordarshan and Ors. MANU/SC/0154/1988; Ram and Shyam Company vs. State of Haryana and Ors. MANU/SC/0017/1985; Haji T.M. Hassan Rawther vs. Kerala Financial Corporation MANU/SC/0516/1987; Food Corporation of India vs. Kamdhenu Cattle Feed Industries MANU/SC/0257/1993; International Airports Authority of India vs. K.D. Bali and Ors. MANU/SC/0197/1988; Union Carbide Corporation and Ors. vs. Union of India (UOI) and Ors. MANU/SC/0058/1992; G. J. Fernandez vs. State of Karnataka and Ors. MANU/SC/0175/1990

